c\Vert g\Vert\leq\Vert T^*\Vert\Vert l\Vert
T
T
c>0
T(\operatorname{Ball}_X)\supset c\operatorname{Ball}_X
 \begin{align} \Vert T^*(g)\Vert &=\sup\{|T^*(g)(x)|:x\in\operatorname{Ball}_X\}\\ &=\sup\{|g(T(x))|:x\in\operatorname{Ball}_X\}\\ &\geq\sup\{|g(y)|:y \in c\operatorname{Ball}_X\}\\ &=c\sup\{|g(y)|:y \in \operatorname{Ball}_X\}\\ &=c\Vert g\Vert \end{align} 
